eedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wnv1665702734401.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wnv1665702734401.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wnv1665702734401.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wnv1665702734401\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      convert numeric\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Enables data to be correctly retrieved when the length of a numeric database field is longer than the length defined in the Uniface field interface definition.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"wnv1665702734401__topic_d59354e1_d59355e1_d59356e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wnv1665702734401__p_d59357e1_d59358e1_d59359e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$SYB_PARAMS</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">= convert numeric</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"wnv1665702734401__section_w3802ab1b5b3_w3803ab1b5_w3804ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wnv1665702734401__p_d59360e1_d59361e1_d59362e1\">This is a compatibility option that is applicable to SYB U5.1 connector and higher. Use this connector option only if you encounter the problem it is designed to solve.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"wnv1665702734401__section_w3805ab1b5b5_w3806ab1b5_w3807ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wnv1665702734401__p_d59363e1_d59364e1_d59365e1\">When using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">convert numeric</span> option, any existing stored procedures must be replaced.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"wnv1665702734401__section_w3808ab1b5b7_w3809ab1b5_w3810ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wnv1665702734401__p_d59366e1_d59367e1_d59368e1\">If U2 stored procedures must be kept in the database, use the Create Table utility with the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">convert numeric</span> connector option to generate an SQL script. Then edit the SQL script to remove the <code class=\"ph codeph\">create table</code> command, leaving the script that will drop and create the stored procedures.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"wnv1665702734401__section_w3811ab1b5b9_w3812ab1b5_w3813ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wnv1665702734401__p_d59369e1_d59370e1_d59371e1\">If no U2 stored procedures need to be kept, use the Create Table facility with both the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">upgrade procs</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">convert numeric</span> options to generate SQL scripts that will drop and create stored procedures.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jyo1665702685940.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Create Table Facility for Sybase</a><p>The Create Table facility (/genSql createtable) is fully supported.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xfd1665702778269.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Sybase Stored Procedures</a><p>The SYB connector supports the use of Sybase stored procedures. These can also be activated as service stored procedures.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/onv1665702969256.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>upgrade procs</a><p>Upgrade Sybase connector U2 stored procedures to match the current version.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533441\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533441\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "convert numeric Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 convert numeric Enables data to be correctly retrieved when the length of a numeric database field is longer than the length defined in the Uniface field interface definition. USYS$SYB_PARAMS = convert numeric This is a compatibility option that is applicable to SYB U5.1 connector and higher. Use this connector option only if you encounter the problem it is designed to solve. When using the convert numeric option, any existing stored procedures must be replaced. If U2 stored procedures must be kept in the database, use the Create Table utility with the convert numeric connector option to generate an SQL script. Then edit the SQL script to remove the create table command, leaving the script that will drop and create the stored procedures. If no U2 stored procedures need to be kept, use the Create Table facility with both the upgrade procs and convert numeric options to generate SQL scripts that will drop and create stored procedures. Related Links Create Table Facility for Sybase The Create Table facility (/genSql createtable) is fully supported. Sybase Stored Procedures The SYB connector supports the use of Sybase stored procedures. These can also be activated as service stored procedures. upgrade procs Upgrade Sybase connector U2 stored procedures to match the current version. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}